            "richtext_content": "<p>Callum Simpson is a dynamic professional boxer making waves in the British boxing scene. Known for his speed, power, and unrelenting work ethic, Callum has quickly established himself as one of the most promising talents in the ring. As a Gym King ambassador, Callum brings the same determination to his training and personal style, embodying the brand’s values of grit, resilience, and ambition.</p>"
