          "type": "quote",
          "settings": {
            "quote_text": "Boxing has always been my passion. From the first time I stepped into the ring, I knew this was my calling. The discipline, the hard work—it’s all part of the process. Being a Gym King ambassador is a huge honor because the brand represents everything I believe in: resilience, hard work, and never giving up.",
